WEBVTT

00:02.095 --> 00:03.529
Previously
on "The Originals"...

00:03.530 --> 00:05.629
This town was my home once.
I want it back.

00:05.630 --> 00:08.301
Our community
is under attack.

00:08.302 --> 00:10.102
Resurrected witches
with vast power?

00:10.103 --> 00:11.261
It's the harvest.

00:11.262 --> 00:13.430
Four girls were
meant to die

00:13.431 --> 00:14.707
and be reborn.

00:14.708 --> 00:16.709
Someone jacked
that power.

00:16.710 --> 00:18.544
I believe that when
you love someone

00:18.545 --> 00:20.713
and that person
loves you in return,

00:20.714 --> 00:22.147
you're uniquely
vulnerable.

00:22.148 --> 00:24.116
Celeste, she died
because of me.

00:24.117 --> 00:25.651
I'd appreciate it if you'd
call me by my real name...

00:26.150 --> 00:27.253
Celeste.

00:27.254 --> 00:28.921
What about Hayley?

00:28.922 --> 00:30.089
None of my treachery
will harm this family

00:30.090 --> 00:31.791
as much as your
feelings for her.

00:31.792 --> 00:33.526
This blade contains

00:33.527 --> 00:35.126
all the power I harvested
from the vampires.

00:35.127 --> 00:36.594
It will do
things worse than death.

00:36.595 --> 00:38.705
And are you ready
for the final offering?

